sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / SDK
    participant GW as Platform Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant ObjStore as S3 / MinIO<br/>9000/443 TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ArgoWF as Argo Workflow
    participant Driver as Driver<br/>(init container)
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant CacheSvr as Cache Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Launcher as Launcher<br/>(user container wrapper)
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SWC as Scheduled Workflow<br/>Controller

    Note over User,Launcher: Flow 1: Pipeline Execution

    User->>GW: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Bearer Token
    GW->>API: Forward (TLS terminated)
    API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>Username/Password
    API->>ObjStore: Store pipeline spec<br/>Access Key / IAM
    API->>K8sAPI: Create Argo Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    K8sAPI->>ArgoWF: Schedule Workflow
    ArgoWF->>Driver: Run init container
    Driver->>MLMD: Create execution context<br/>gRPC (Optional TLS)
    Driver->>API: Cache check (TaskService)<br/>gRPC/8887 Bearer Token
    API-->>Driver: Cache hit/miss
    Driver->>K8sAPI: Read ConfigMaps, manage PVCs<br/>ServiceAccount

    Note over K8sAPI,CacheSvr: Flow 4: Cache Mutation (parallel)
    K8sAPI->>CacheSvr: AdmissionReview (pod create)<br/>HTTPS/443→8443
    CacheSvr->>DB: Cache lookup<br/>Username/Password
    CacheSvr-->>K8sAPI: Mutated pod spec (cached results)

    Note over Driver,Launcher: Pipeline Step Execution
    Driver-->>Launcher: Pod spec patched with inputs
    Launcher->>ObjStore: Download input artifacts<br/>Access Key / IAM
    Launcher->>Launcher: Execute user code
    Launcher->>ObjStore: Upload output artifacts<br/>Access Key / IAM
    Launcher->>MLMD: Publish execution results<br/>gRPC (Optional TLS)

    Note over PA,API: Flow 3: State Persistence (continuous)
    PA->>K8sAPI: Watch Argo Workflows<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>PA: Workflow state changes
    PA->>API: ReportWorkflow<br/>gRPC/8887 Bearer Token (SA)
    API->>DB: Persist execution state<br/>Username/Password

    Note over SWC,API: Flow 2: Scheduled Execution (periodic)
    SWC->>K8sAPI: Watch ScheduledWorkflows<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>SWC: Schedule trigger
    SWC->>API: CreateRun<br/>gRPC/8887 Bearer Token (SA)
    API->>K8sAPI: Create Argo Workflow CR
